  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 947c76105d7454747a8fc8874cd8bff8, type: 3}
  m_Name: OMorning 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NarrationLines
  lines:
  - I enter the office and sit down and my phone begins ringing. It's my boss
  - "\u201CYo, word around the block is that you seem to be taking on Ms Slitmouth.
    And by yourself? You got anything to say for yourself newbie?\u201D"
  - "\u201CI accepted the contract cause I didn\u2019t think much of it. But she
    got away.\u201D I reply."
  - "\u201CYeah don\u2019t beat yourself up about it. She is a tricky one to deal
    with. Even experienced exorcists struggle with taking her down. "
  - "The commission gives you a full day to deal with these things before they\u2019re
    given over to someone else, so you still have time."
  - "Anyways I got my own stuff to deal with so I\u2019ll catch you later.\u201D"
  - He drops the phone and leaves me to sit in silence for a bit.
  - Time to head out.
  line: 
